This paper discusses a data poisoning attack on collaborative filtering systems, which is a topic related to machine learning and security. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.CR (Cryptography and Security), cs.IR (Information Retrieval), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), and cs.SI (Social and Information Networks).
